t: "and a pair of camels and a pair of oxen. Ask ňĻthemňļ, ‚ÄúHas He forbidden ňĻto youňļ the two males or the two females or what is in the wombs of the two females? Or were you present when Allah gave you this commandment?‚ÄĚ Who does more wrong than those who fabricate lies against Allah to mislead others without ňĻanyňļ knowledge? Surely Allah does not guide the wrongdoing people"